      "date": "2012-05-17 19:34:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(2 inline comments)\n\nUnfortunately(?), you refreshed the dependent patches too quickly, and I didn't get a chance to comment on this one before it was updated.\n\nThe liblustre.h problem needs to be resolved before this patch can be landed.\n\nI'm also worried that this patch is so large that it will have repeated conflicts with some other patch that is landed before it, so it probably makes sense to split it up into a few smaller patches (e.g. lnet, ldlm, obdclass, ptlrpc) so that at least some parts can land even if another part has a conflict.",
